Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • Event
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Lecture, Seminar, Trip, Workshop

    public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    A class which represents every common attribute that the four types of events have { @see Lecture, @see Seminar, @see Workshop or @see Trip}
    Author:
    Stefan Harabagiu
